<header class="page-header">
  <h3>Hello! Welcome to suitor.</h3>
  <h1>Let&rsquo;s find you a job.</h1>
</header>

<div class="intro primary">
  <h3>Get your foot in the door, not in your mouth.</h3>
  
  <p>Job-hunting is a pain in the butt. Whether you send out ten resumes or ten hundred, it&rsquo;s important to keep track of your process. Using suitor, you can easily track your application status, send follow-ups, and keep a record of what you said to who, so you&rsquo;ll never accidentally say the wrong thing to the wrong person.</p>

  <% unless current_user %>
    <%= link_to t("Get a free account"), signup_path, class: "primary" %>
    <h3><span>or</span></h3>
    <%= link_to "Log in", login_path, class: "secondary" %>
  <% else %>
    <%= link_to "Log out", logout_path, method: 'delete' %>
  <% end %>
</div>
